Package: yehUtil
Title: Personal package for storing some personalized Rmarkdown templates
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Chi-Kuang",
           family = "Yeh",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "chi-kuang.yeh@uwaterloo.ca",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7057-2096"))
Description: This package contains some Rmarkdown templates custome for personal use, including: 1) A PDF format with a Table of contents with a default font size of 11pt, 2) A dark theme HTML created based on 'downcute' theme in 'rmdformats' package with a Table of contents and code folding option, 3) A RMarkdown template for parallel computing with my own style based on the R package 'lapply'.
